Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:02:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bring the ship forward!\N--You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't shake things, Sanji!\N--Full speed ahead to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. If you're scared, then go\Ndown and sleep like a good li'l boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't be stupid!\NOf course I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji! Breakfast!\N--Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get started on it. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hey, Zoro. Let's play tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?! Tag?!\NLet's play, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid?!\NYou're pathetic, playing at your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get some more\Nsleep before breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! 'Cause you\Ndon't like losing, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!\NI don't give a damn about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See! You're suddenly mad!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth, isn't it?! Bleehhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll\Njoin our crew now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm only teaming up\Nwith you, just so you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm over here! Come get me!\N--C'mon, Zoro! Chase me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Your meal's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Food's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I'm not done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he said all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what do you suppose\Nhappened to Buggy after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy? Oh, that Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe he's\Nat the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are a stubborn lot,\Nevery last one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:04:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who kept\Nchasing me stubbornly! Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hunted pirates for years. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it matters,\Nbut your food's gone, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you are, Nami-san!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A Special Yogurt Dessert!\N--You stole my food again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! Thank you, Sanji-kun!\N--Give it back, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally finished my flashy raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the great and world-renowned\Npirate, Buggy the Clown-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will get my crew back together\Nand get my super flashy revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what obstacles lie in my path!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The score must be settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn flashy\Nrubber man! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will beat you senseless\Nand make you cry uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like this already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to lose! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chase Straw Hat!\NLittle Buggy's Big Adventure"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to make it...\Nto the next island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not some kind of exhibit, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! Are you mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some real guts, ridiculing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eatcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just feeling hungry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me mad!\NYou're done for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat you flashily,\Nso just give yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your flailing!\NJust accept your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! Yum! Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did things turn out this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end already?! This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! Am I that bad-tasting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little bit of a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! A hermit crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when he got on\Nboard. At Nami's village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. That, or maybe\Nat Usopp's village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, that's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd mean he's been\Ntraveling with us this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why does this happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did you just say something?\N--Huh? Me? I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. Must've\Nbeen my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Luffy! Quit slackin' off!\N--Oh! Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am this island's protective god!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island at once\Nif you value your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protective god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! You're one of those, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...weird creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your ass, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Just try taking\Nanother step into the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant you do, will you\Nreceive my divine punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and meet your doom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know, you flashy idiot?!\NWhy're you asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The animals of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with them,\Nunless you want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? These are some\Nflashily interesting animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast it! He suddenly shot at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come out!\N--Oww! Oww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! You have a Devil Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I do?! You're nothing--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a boxed and sheltered son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've been overly pampered\Nsince I was just a little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do stupid gags!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't show mercy to anyone\Nwho messes with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You wanna fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I commend your bravery,\Nbut don't blame me after you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying weapons are unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's this thing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so selfishly!\NSay your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How dare you?! Blast it! Oww!\N--How dare I what?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! Anyone who messes\Nwith the animals has to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're this island's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those weird animals are treasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure refers to gold, silver,\Nand jewels, you flashy idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play stupid! You came to\Nthis island to get these animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do that?! I didn't\Ncome here 'cause I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're not a poacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I might not\Nlook it, but I'm a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Buggy the Clown-sama!\NI'd never do anything as mean as that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate? You're a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! I used to be a\Npirate a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad! My bad!\NSo you're a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya think? Good, huh?!\NIt's my own unrefined sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the best! How many\Ndays it's been since I last drank...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have as many refills\Nas you want! Drink up and up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really sorry about earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed you were a poacher\Nwho came to get these animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some horrible stuff you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus you let me have\Nthis delicious booze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things in this world that\Ninterest me are treasure and alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm likin' you even more!\NYou're a pirate, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real stout-hearted guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, why are you on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I originally came here\Nin search of treasure, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There's treasure on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. If there was, I wouldn't\Nbe hanging around here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, some stuff happened\Nand my crew left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been calling this island\Nhome for the past 20 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really had it rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad, really.\NThese guys are here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way of life is actually pretty\Nnice once you get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. I'd much rather be living\Nthe pirate life with my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, pirate life is nice! It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I would gladly risk my life to\Ngo on treasure-hunting adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! It's like, "Hurray for pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? When I get my\Npirate crew back, won't you join us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I greatly welcome guys like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you have the pirate spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Whadya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... inviting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought,\Nbut these guys are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you live with them for\N20 years, they rub off on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they are weird creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just\Nremembering a young pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who asked me to be a pirate\Nagain just like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so upset, old guy!\NIt's a good thing we came after 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 years later and you\Nmight've been dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was such an incredibly nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you and him'd be good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So there are\Nyoungsters out there like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me, though.\NI ran into this one horrible kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble! Chop-Chop Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go flying, Buggy! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I wound up\Non a wandering journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about it now\Nmakes me boil with rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sorry to hear what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it just goes to show there are\Nall kinds of youngsters out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's have fun tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want this\Nnight to go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--To pirates!\N--And to us meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for asking you\Nto help make a raft, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really going to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. With all my friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, friend! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many strange\Ncreatures in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ever careful on your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I forgot to tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Look out! Run! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's super pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least it looks like he's saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had me sweating bullets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help! I flashily\Nthought I was a goner there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Buggy the Clown, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:21:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Someday, I will settle\Nthe score with you! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guy you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. I have a meal ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why you helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you say?\NWill you team up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?\NWe both have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. Then cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji... Food...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just ate... Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys... I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep too much... Help out\Nwith work sometimes... Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed they can hold\Nconversations in their sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about skillful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.01,0:22:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll hit the hay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Buggy's\Nhenchmen were neat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you mean like the\Nunicycle guy and the lion guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cabaji and Mohji, was it?\N--He had animals, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.45,0:24:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is their captain now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji or Mohji, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe it's that lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wait is Over!\NThe Return of Captain Buggy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
